                    "type": "AssignmentExpression",
                    "name": "innerHTML",
                    "source": "\n        <p>\\u26A0\\uFE0F <strong>Deprecation Warning</strong>: <code>renderHeatmapTrackerLegend</code> is deprecated.</p>\n        <p>Please use <code>renderHeatmapTracker</code> with <code>ui.defaultView</code> set to <code>'legend'</code> instead.</p>\n        <p><strong>Example:</strong></p>\n        <pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">\n        const trackerData = {\n          // ... other properties,\n          ui: {\n            defaultView: 'legend'\n          }\n        }\n        renderHeatmapTracker(this.container, trackerData);\n        </code></pre>\n      ",
                    "target": "\n        <p>\\u26A0\\uFE0F <strong>弃用警告</strong>: <code>renderHeatmapTrackerLegend</code> 已弃用。</p>\n        <p>请改用 <code>renderHeatmapTracker</code>，并将 <code>ui.defaultView</code> 设置为 <code>'legend'</code>。</p>\n        <p><strong>示例：</strong></p>\n        <pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">\n        const trackerData = {\n          // ... other properties,\n          ui: {\n            defaultView: 'legend'\n          }\n        }\n        renderHeatmapTracker(this.container, trackerData);\n        </code></pre>\n      "
                },
                {
                    "type": "AssignmentExpression",
                    "name": "innerHTML",
                    "source": "\n        <p>\\u26A0\\uFE0F <strong>Deprecation Warning</strong>: <code>renderHeatmapTrackerStatistics</code> is deprecated.</p>\n        <p>Please use <code>renderHeatmapTracker</code> with <code>ui.defaultView</code> set to <code>'heatmap-tracker-statistics'</code> instead.</p>\n        <p><strong>Example:</strong></p>\n        <pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">\n        const trackerData = {\n          // ... other properties,\n          ui: {\n            defaultView: 'heatmap-tracker-statistics'\n          }\n        }\n        renderHeatmapTracker(this.container, trackerData);\n        </code></pre>\n      ",
                    "target": "\n        <p>\\u26A0\\uFE0F <strong>弃用警告</strong>: <code>renderHeatmapTrackerStatistics</code> 已弃用。</p>\n        <p>请改用 <code>renderHeatmapTracker</code>，并将 <code>ui.defaultView</code> 设置为 <code>'heatmap-tracker-statistics'</code>。</p>\n        <p><strong>示例：</strong></p>\n        <pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">\n        const trackerData = {\n          // ... other properties,\n          ui: {\n            defaultView: 'heatmap-tracker-statistics'\n          }\n        }\n        renderHeatmapTracker(this.container, trackerData);\n        </code></pre>\n      "
